$ Licenses

CPOL: → https://www.codeproject.com/info/cpol10.aspx[The Code Project Open License]

CC0: public domain

BY
-
BY-SA
-
BY-NC
-
BY-NC-SA
-
BY-ND
-
BY-NC-ND

*BY* means that attribution is required.
-
*ND* means that no derivatives are allowed.
-
*NC* means that it is for non commercial use
-
*SA* stands for share alike.


{ Open source licensces

  Two types of → development/open-source[Open source] licenses:
    • Permissive licenses
    • Copyleft licenses

  Typically, permissive licenses require to include two artifacts in the redistribution:
    • the original copyright notice and
    • a copy of the license text

  Copyleft add the requirement to also offer the source code of any modifications to all recipients of the binary. The modified source code must have the same license.

}

